Package: tweetbotornot2
Title: Detect Twitter Bots
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael W.", "Kearney", ,
      email = "kearneymw@missouri.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0730-4694"))
Description: This package provides an out-of-the-box classifier for detecting Twitter bots
    that is easy to use, volume-friendly (classify over two hundred thousands accounts per day),
    accurate (see paper), robust and customizable (update the model with new or user-defined training data),
    and explainable (view contributions for features used in estimates).
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
